source ยท 
pub trait OnGenesis {
    // Provided method
    fn on_genesis() { ... }

Expand description

A trait that will be called at genesis.

Implementing this trait for a pallet letโs you express operations that should happen at genesis. It will be called in an externalities provided environment and will set the genesis state after all pallets have written their genesis state.
